=head1 DESCRIPTION

HLS playlist configuration parameters.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 AdMarkupType => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

Determines the type of SCTE 35 tags to use in ad markup. Specify
C<DATERANGE> to use C<DATERANGE> tags (for live or VOD content).
Specify C<SCTE35_ENHANCED> to use C<EXT-X-CUE-OUT> and C<EXT-X-CUE-IN>
tags (for VOD content only).


=head2 ManifestWindowSeconds => Int

The total duration (in seconds) of each manifest. Minimum value: C<30>
seconds. Maximum value: C<3600> seconds.



